ed91f","tid":1293243,"uid":259842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"95f66a36d51740db17fd1f4211a5134367b42c40","tid":1293243,"uid":260251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f756e9cd5e66db286d129b9019cbeeefefe98cac","tid":1293243,"uid":234831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"請記得，大家若果被捕，是有權打給律師的。若擔心屆時未能打電話，建議你將自己的：<br />\n中英文全名、<br />\n身份證號碼、<br />\n年齡、<br />\n聯絡電話<br />\n等資料，預先交託給可靠的朋友，朋友一旦發現你被捕，就可以代你聯絡律師。<br />\n<br />\n各位保重。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n反送中傷者被捕者人道支援基金：<br />\n9845 6641 （致電/sms）<br />\n<br />\n被捕支援<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察 <br />\n9463 2945（tg/sms/whatsapp）<br />\n民陣 <br />\n6549 9452 (whatsapp/telegram/sms)<br />\n伍展邦律師 <br />\n@hksup（tg) / 5690 2877（whatsapp） / 2608 1400<br />\n<br />\n韋智達律師 9167 7091<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟 （fb inbox）<br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線 <br />\n5934 5588 (whatsapp/sms) @Hkibackup （tg)<br />\n<br />\n港大 9139 0589<br />\n中大 9443 3459<br />\n科大 6019 6339 / 2335 1732 / 2335 5672<br />\n浸大 6110 3860<br />\n城大 9545 4172 / 3442 5570<br />\n理大 6800 0560 / 2766 7025 / 6253 2359<br />\n教大 5108 3519<br />\n演藝 6679 0772 / 9464 5078<br />\n<br />\n如見抗爭者被捕，請大家連同以下資料，聯絡上述單位：<br />\n1. 被捕者中文姓名<br />\n2. 被捕者英文姓名<br />\n3. 被捕者身份證號碼<br />\n4. 被捕者乘坐之警車號碼 / 所在警署"},{"pid":"6b19e922b4431888d24fc5e409dfc847707c055a","tid":1293243,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"171ab270323fd61df9ba41945829ed3393aae971","tid":1293243,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df25c9b5c85e31cf1cea50781bde1013bd8d5747","tid":1293243,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a5780e0adc757d11b07ad69d17ca25bcfee1cf","tid":1293243,"uid":158615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/224053934470547/posts/1149913818551216/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F224053934470547%2Fposts%2F1149913818551216%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=2994ad95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/224053934470547/posts/1149913818551216/</a><br />\n<br />\n【緊急】<br />\n<br />\n今晚盡力頂眼瞓開放睇病，我地真係好鍾意睇病。<br />\n<br />\n新時代睇病，時間地點負責醫師全部行雲流水冇路捉，總之發夢受傷就係同病相憐嘅朋友，雖然萍水相逢，免費睇個病都係情義，有咩pm。<br />\n<br />\n最鍾意睇嘅病種：<br />\n扭傷、撞傷、打傷、硬物擊傷（唔知邊個咁暴力夜媽媽打人）<br />\n拉傷、跌傷<br />\n化學物品刺激傷<br />\n關節脫位、懷疑骨折等<br />\n亦可判斷傷勢和建議治療選項<br />\n心靈受創、精神壓力難以承受，一樣歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n長為有夢想的人開放。<br />\n<br />\n（有我真人識你o既醫師未訓有興趣睇病都pm下，可以一齊standby，結交朋友係人類o既溫馨。）<br />\n<br />\n#做香港人真係好很攰"},{"pid":"99270b86430b3dc4240158f9fef35d314cd95251","tid":1293243,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"現場有藍絲打人<br />\n班狗咩都唔做"},{"pid":"cb179e2a53351217d643ea8c9fcf03edd3a333ac","tid":1293243,"uid":270456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7bb22edd5c1dbd9d3ab4fbe68e0988224a15ca","tid":1293243,"uid":141266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:11:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d79b67ccd5b8facf2cc0f51621d060daf4314597","tid":1293243,"uid":210469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"啲仆街黑警無人性架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset